        <h2> Black Sesame Seeds:</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Sesame seeds, especially the black sesame, are known to blacken the hair. Hence, they can be applied to white hair.
            Eating some black sesame seeds twice a week may help to slow down or even reverse the hair greying process.
            Black sesame seeds can help combat damage to cells in your body which causes gray hair, hair loss</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Mix half a cup of sesame seeds with 4 tbsp of yoghurt and 1 tbsp of honey.</li>
            <li>Apply to hair and leave for 30 minutes.</li>
            <li>Rinse and use your favourite conditioner.</li>
        </ol>
