             Dried fruit of amla and coconut oil can be boiled together till it gets charred and used to prevent hair greying.
             Drink amla juice regularly to avoid premature greying of hair.</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>To make the hair pack, take a bunch of curry leaves and grind them with 2 tablespoons of amla powder and 2 tablespoons of brahmi powder.</li>
